                  "blocks": {
                    "text_eDTcCA": {
                      "type": "text",
                      "settings": {
                        "custom_class": "",
                        "text": "<p><strong>Clean Skin Application:</strong> Apply to clean, dry skin so the serum can spread evenly.</p><p><strong>Face & Neck Coverage:</strong> Use a small amount across the face and neck, avoiding the eye area.</p><p><strong>Target Aging Zones:</strong> Focus on wrinkles, fine lines, dull areas, and uneven-looking tone.</p><p><strong>Morning & Evening Use:</strong> Apply twice daily for consistent visible anti-aging support.</p><p><strong>Moisturizer Pairing:</strong> Follow with moisturizer to help seal hydration and support smoothness.</p>",
